## Copy to .env and fill your details
## Gmail example (enable 2FA, generate App Password):
# EMAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# EMAIL_PORT=587
# EMAIL_USER=your@gmail.com
# EMAIL_PASS=your-16-char-app-password

## Ethereal test (dev only, check ethereal.email inbox):
# Use fallback code or manual:
# EMAIL_HOST=smtp.ethereal.email
# EMAIL_PORT=587
# EMAIL_USER=testuser
# EMAIL_PASS=testpass

## Local Postfix (if you have it running):
# EMAIL_HOST=127.0.0.1
# EMAIL_PORT=587
# EMAIL_USER=
